      "text": "// Struct with generics\nstruct Point<T> { x: T, y: T }\n\n// Trait definition\ntrait Drawable {\n    fn draw(&self);\n    fn render() { println!(\"Rendering\"); }\n}\n\n// Enum with variants\nenum Message {\n    Quit,\n    Move { x: i32, y: i32 },\n    Write(String),\n}",
